P_HTM[1872]='****** 602*. Tena ** samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. Tena kho ** pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū asakkaccaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggaṇhanti chaḍḍetukāmā viya…pe….*';
P_HTM[1873]='** ‘‘Sakkaccaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggahessāmīti sikkhā karaṇīyā’’*ti.*';
P_HTM[1874]='* Sakkaccaṃ piṇḍapāto paṭiggahetabbo. Yo anādariyaṃ paṭicca asakkaccaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggaṇhāti chaḍḍetukāmo viya, āpatti dukkaṭassa.*';
