P_HTM[1879]='* Pattasaññinā piṇḍapāto paṭiggahetabbo. Yo anādariyaṃ paṭicca tahaṃ tahaṃ olokento piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggaṇhāti, āpatti dukkaṭassa.*';
