P_HTM[1881]='* Aṭṭhamasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1882]='****** 604*. Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggaṇhantā sūpaññeva bahuṃ paṭiggaṇhanti…pe….*';
P_HTM[1883]='** ‘‘Samasūpakaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggahessāmīti sikkhā karaṇīyā’’*ti.*';
P_HTM[1884]='** Sūpo* nāma dve sūpā – muggasūpo, māsasūpo. Hatthahāriyo samasūpako piṇḍapāto paṭiggahetabbo. Yo anādariyaṃ paṭicca sūpaññeva bahuṃ paṭiggaṇhāti, āpatti dukkaṭassa.*';
P_HTM[1885]='* Anāpatti asañcicca, assatiyā, ajānantassa, gilānassa, rasarase, ñātakānaṃ pavāritānaṃ, aññassatthāya, attano dhanena, āpadāsu, ummattakassa, ādikammikassāti.*';
P_HTM[1886]='* Navamasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1887]='****** 605*. Tena *samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū thūpīkataṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggaṇhanti…pe….*';
P_HTM[1888]='** ‘‘Samatittikaṃ* *[samatitthikaṃ (ka.)]* *piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggahessāmīti sikkhā karaṇīyā’’*ti.*';
P_HTM[1889]='* Samatittiko ** *[samatitthikaṃ (ka.)]* piṇḍapāto paṭiggahetabbo. Yo anādariyaṃ paṭicca thūpīkataṃ piṇḍapātaṃ paṭiggaṇhāti, āpatti dukkaṭassa.*';
