P_HTM[1891]='* Dasamasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[1892]='* Khambhakatavaggo tatiyo.*';
P_HTM[1893]='* 4. Sakkaccavaggo*';
P_HTM[1894]='****** 606*. Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū asakkaccaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjanti abhuñjitukāmā viya…pe….*';
P_HTM[1895]='** ‘‘Sakkaccaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjissāmīti sikkhā karaṇīyā’’*ti.*';
P_HTM[1896]='* Sakkaccaṃ piṇḍapāto bhuñjitabbo. Yo anādariyaṃ paṭicca asakkaccaṃ piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjati, āpatti dukkaṭassa.*';
P_HTM[1897]='* Anāpatti asañcicca, assatiyā, ajānantassa, gilānassa, āpadāsu, ummattakassa,*';
P_HTM[1898]='* Ādikammikassāti.*';
P_HTM[1899]='* Paṭhamasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.*';
