P_HTM[1905]='****** 608*. Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū tahaṃ tahaṃ omasitvā *[omadditvā (ka.)]* piṇḍapātaṃ bhuñjanti…pe….*';
