P_HTM[2002]='****** 627*. Tena samayena buddho bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme. Tena kho pana samayena aññatarena brāhmaṇena saṅghassa payopānaṃ paṭiyattaṃ hoti. Bhikkhū surusurukārakaṃ khīraṃ pivanti. Aññataro naṭapubbako bhikkhu evamāha – ‘‘sabboyaṃ maññe saṅgho sītīkato’’ti. Ye te bhikkhū appicchā…pe… te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti – ‘‘kathañhi nāma bhikkhu saṅghaṃ ārabbha davaṃ karissatī’’ti…pe… saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, saṅghaṃ ārabbha davaṃ akāsīti? ‘‘Saccaṃ, bhagavā’’ti. Vigarahi buddho bhagavā…pe… kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, saṅghaṃ ārabbha davaṃ karissasi! Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya…pe… vigarahitvā…pe… dhammiṃ kathaṃ katvā bhikkhū āmantesi – ‘‘na, bhikkhave, buddhaṃ vā dhammaṃ vā ** saṅghaṃ vā ārabbha davo kātabbo. Yo kareyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā’’ti. Atha kho bhagavā taṃ bhikkhuṃ anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā dubbharatāya…pe… evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha –*';
